Park. ; Photo, An overview of grassy Horton Plaza Park, which attracts drug 
dealers and panhandlers who repel shoppers at the plaza, officials say. ; 
Photo, Although benches have been removed, people find alternative places to 
sit, or lie, at Horton Plaza Park. TERESA TAMURA / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
