<DATE>
<P>
March 13, 1990, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 3; Column 6; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
