<TEXT>
<P>
Ivan Lendl of Czechoslovakia, the world's top-ranked player, and last year's 
French Open champion, Michael Chang of Placentia, Calif., will lead a field of 
56 in the $1.15-million Suntory Japan Tennis Championship April 9 through 15. 
</P>
