<TEXT>
<P>
Sure Sign will be looking for her third win of the year when she takes on a 
tough field of seven in the $3,600 distaff pacing feature Wednesday night at 
Los Alamitos. 
</P>
<P>
The eighth race main event is a claiming handicap with the prices ranging from 
$6,000 to $8,000. Starlitas, Palladay Road, Sassy Sapphire and Call Holding 
receive an age allowance and race with a claiming price of $7,500. 
</P>
